<li class='cover' id='bookCover_53746807'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53746807-sparks-like-stars"><img alt="Sparks Like Stars" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1608625584l/53746807._SX98_.jpg" />
